title: The Lost Skeleton Returns Again
actors: H.M. Wynant, Frank Dietz, Christine Romeo, Brian Howe
plot: Jerranium 90, a "little rock" that made all the papers, is buried deep within the Amazon. And everybody wants it, including crooked importer Handscomb Draile, slimy Gondreau Slykes, cheap crook Carl Traeger and evil scientist Dr. Ellamy Royne.
